[2] Florida
Date: 16 Jun 2021
Source: EquiManagment [edited]
https://equimanagement.com/news/fifth-confirmed-2021-case-of-eastern-equine-encephalitis-in-florida


The Florida Department of Agriculture and Consumer Services confirmed a case of EEE in a horse at a private facility in Levy County. Three other horses were exposed. This is the 5th confirmed case of EEE in Florida this year [2021].

[Byline: Kimberly S. Brown]

